name: FindDuplicatesResult

fields.name: duplicateresults
fields.description: A list of DuplicateResult objects representing the results of calling FindDuplicates.findDuplicates(sObjects) or FindDuplicatesByIds.findDuplicatesByIds(ids). Elements in the list correspond to sObjects or IDs in the input list.

fields.name: errors
fields.description: A list of Database.Error objects holding errors resulting from calling FindDuplicates.findDuplicates(sObjects) or FindDuplicatesByIds.findDuplicatesByIds(ids).

fields.name: success
fields.description: Boolean signifying whether the call to FindDuplicates.findDuplicates(sObjects) or FindDuplicatesByIds.findDuplicatesByIds(ids) was successful.

methods.name: getDuplicateResults
methods.description: Returns  a list of DuplicateResult objects representing the results of calling FindDuplicates.findDuplicates(sObjects) or FindDuplicatesByIds.findDuplicatesByIds(ids). Elements in the list correspond to sObjects or IDs in the input list.

methods.name: getErrors
methods.description: Returns a list of DatabaseError objects containing errors resulting from calling FindDuplicates.findDuplicates(sObjects) or FindDuplicatesByIds.findDuplicatesByIds(ids), if errors were encountered.

methods.name: isSuccess
methods.description: Returns a Boolean signifying whether the call to FindDuplicates.findDuplicates(sObjects) or FindDuplicatesByIds.findDuplicatesByIds(ids) was successful.

description: Output for rule-based searches for duplicate records. FindDuplicatesResult contains results of detecting duplicates using instances of FindDuplicates or FindDuplicatesByIds classes.
